1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by
year after year of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
I can do nothing but feign indifference

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,820
[Episode 3]

19
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,160
My face.

20
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,080
There's a dead woman.

21
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,830
Shangguan Zhi, what are you up to?

22
00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:43,000
I will replace you as Mrs. Pan.

23
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,080
You shall replace me
as I die for the sake of love.

24
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,390
Your coffin is already prepared.

25
00:02:58,470 --> 00:02:59,630
Shangguan Zhi

26
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:02,000
swapped her face with mine
and went to the wedding.

27
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,800
I have to stop her.

28
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,830
Yue,

29
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,720
you belong to me eventually.

30
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:12,600
Groom, let me offer you a toast.

31
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,270
May you enjoy deep affection

32
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:16,950
and experience eternal love.

33
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,230
Thank you.

34
00:04:24,790 --> 00:04:27,350
Sir, Master sent his men here.

35
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:31,350
Please have a seat.
I'll be back in a second.

36
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:32,640
All right. Please go ahead.

37
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,720
Here.

38
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,270
Mr. Shangguan,

39
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:48,970
Young Lady told someone
to deliver this to you.

40
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:52,600
[Lan]

41
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,480
Today, I've lost my beloved.

42
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:57,000
There's no point in living.

43
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:58,950
Lan, please don't miss me.

44
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,790
Relay my order.

45
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,480
Locate her at all costs even if it means

46
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:03,640
you have to search the entire Heyang.

47
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,110
Yes, Mr. Shangguan.

48
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:09,700
[Sunrise Garden]

49
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:20,760
This is bad.

50
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,550
The wedding is already over.

51
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,040
Shangguan Zhi.

52
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,440
What's wrong?

53
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,230
Is that Pan Yue?

54
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:06,830
Someone! Help!

55
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,110
The bride jumped off the building!

56
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,040
Someone!

57
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:11,830
Someone!

58
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:47,380
[The lone daughter
of the Yang family is dead]

59
00:08:48,470 --> 00:08:51,350
Mr. Pan, I have to thank you for this.

60
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,910
Pan Yue?

61
00:09:39,590 --> 00:09:40,400
You!

62
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,150
You have to die.

63
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,640
Young Lady!

64
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:55,910
Young Lady!

65
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:57,840
Young Lady?

66
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,320
Young Lady!

67
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,880
[One month later]

68
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,670
Young Lady.

69
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,710
Young Lady!

70
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,470
Young Lady!

71
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:07,760
Mr. Shangguan, she's awake.

72
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,350
Zhi, how do you feel?

73
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:10,440
Do you feel better?

74
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,280
Who are you?

75
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:19,590
You can still joke around, huh?

76
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,030
I'm your elder brother.

77
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,080
Zhi.

78
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,440
Don't come near me.

79
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,910
Did he call me Zhi?

80
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:49,200
I will replace you as Mrs. Pan.

81
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,590
You shall replace me
as I die for the sake of love.

82
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:55,280
I'm the daughter of Yang Ji'an,

83
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,350
Yang Caiwei!

84
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,960
Become the true Yang Caiwei.

85
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,550
Zhi,

86
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,150
you haven't fully recovered yet.

87
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,150
I'll bring you to your room.

88
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:04,670
Come on.

89
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,520
Don't touch me!

90
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:08,880
I'm not Shangguan Zhi.

91
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,590
Physician,

92
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,790
didn't you say Zhi was fine?

93
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,000
Why is she acting like this?

94
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,200
Mr. Shangguan,

95
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:19,960
there's nothing to worry
about Young Lady's injury.

96
00:11:20,350 --> 00:11:22,230
However, she was in a coma
for one month after all.

97
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:24,710
I'm afraid her mental state
has been damaged.

98
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,080
Help the Young Lady to get on the bed.

99
00:11:27,110 --> 00:11:28,350
I'll administer
the acupuncture treatment.

100
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:31,960
Don't come near me!

101
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,520
You guys should leave first.

102
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,640
I need some time alone.

103
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:43,840
Ling,

104
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,670
take them outside.

105
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,880
Yes, Mr. Shangguan.

106
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:50,350
Zhi,

107
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,960
rest well.

108
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,840
I'll visit you later.

109
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,400
I was actually in a coma for one month?

110
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,520
Now, all of them think
I'm Shangguan Zhi.

111
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,960
What should I do?

112
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:25,000
I would've been dead

113
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,910
if Shangguan Zhi
hadn't swapped her face with mine.

114
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:29,960
What exactly happened that night?

115
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,400
I cannot reveal my identity recklessly

116
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,470
without knowing the truth.

117
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:36,230
Right now,

118
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,440
I have to escape

119
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:37,960
as soon as possible.

120
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,840
Young Lady, time to wash up.

121
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,110
Come in.

122
00:13:13,350 --> 00:13:14,550
Young Lady, what's wrong?

123
00:13:15,230 --> 00:13:16,150
It's nothing.

124
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,590
By the way,

125
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
doesn't this room

126
00:13:22,350 --> 00:13:23,150
belong to Pan...

127
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,880
I mean, doesn't this room belong to Yue?

128
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,080
What are we doing here?

129
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:28,590
Young Lady, the physician said

130
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:30,710
we shouldn't move you around
when you were in a coma.

131
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:32,230
That's why Mr. Shangguan
bought this place.

132
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,030
Where's Yue, then?

133
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,840
He returned to the capital
one month ago.

134
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:42,030
Young Lady, here.

135
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:42,710
I can do it myself.

136
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,790
We deserve to die!

137
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:49,000
Young Lady, please punish us!

138
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,320
Wait.

139
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,440
What do you guys mean?

140
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,760
Young Lady, you only smile at us

141
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:58,400
when you're furious.

142
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:00,400
Usually, the consequences

143
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:01,590
are worse

144
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,150
than when you're angry at us.

145
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,520
I'm not angry at you guys.

146
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,470
You guys should get up first.

147
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,910
We deserve to die!

148
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,960
Young Lady, please punish us!

149
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,910
Is there no authority to my words now?

150
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,350
You guys better get up!

151
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:25,840
Ling.

152
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,350
Young Lady, do you need anything?

153
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:31,230
I remember
that Yue was holding his wedding

154
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:32,910
before I fell into a coma.

155
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:34,710
What happened after that?

156
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,230
Miss Yang took her own life
by jumping off the building

157
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:40,000
on the night of the wedding.

158
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:41,760
Why would she take her own life?

159
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:44,470
I mean,

160
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:47,150
she was able to get married to Yue.

161
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:49,280
Why would she take her own life?

162
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,320
I heard

163
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:51,440
that Miss Yang

164
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,150
was the only person
in the room back then.

165
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,110
After that, the county magistrate
even launched an investigation.

166
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:57,150
Even so, there was
nothing abnormal about it.

167
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,230
That's why everyone was speculating

168
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:00,550
that Miss Yang took her own life

169
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,110
from the pressure she faced

170
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,670
when she was getting married to Mr. Pan.

171
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,760
Where did they bury her body, then?

172
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,280
Did they transport it
back to the capital?

173
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,640
I don't know about that.

174
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:12,550
At first, Mr. Shangguan
wanted to help them out.

175
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:14,520
But Mr. Pan said

176
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,350
that Miss Yang was already buried.

177
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,520
That quickly?

178
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:20,080
And they were being secretive too.

179
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:22,710
Could it be that Pan Yue was afraid
that he left some evidence behind?

180
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:32,320
What is this?

181
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,000
Young Lady, did you forget?

182
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:36,000
This is the prescription given to you
by the witch healer.

183
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:37,670
You have to drink it every night.

184
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:40,910
It's goat placenta
cooked with plain water.

185
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:43,080
It invigorates the skin
and enhances one's complexion.

186
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:44,840
Young Lady, drink it while it's hot.

187
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,910
No thanks.

188
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:47,670
I won't be having it.

189
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:49,790
I just feel like

190
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,440
I already had a narrow escape.

191
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,960
There's no need for me to torture myself

192
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,640
with such weird items.

193
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,400
You can take it away.

194
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,520
Yes, Young Lady.

195
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:09,350
What kind of rule is this?

196
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,790
Do you want a reward?

197
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,150
I deserve to die!

198
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,150
Young Lady, please punish me!

199
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:21,000
It's wrong again.

200
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:22,960
That's right! It's all my fault
for getting it wrong!

201
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,230
I wasn't referring to you.

202
00:16:24,230 --> 00:16:25,000
It was me.

203
00:16:25,590 --> 00:16:27,000
Why did you extend your hand?

204
00:16:27,110 --> 00:16:28,590
Young Lady, you can only sleep

205
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,960
after taking off your clothes

206
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,280
before you sleep, right?

207
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:34,440
I was waiting for your clothing.

208
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,910
I feel unwell today.

209
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,790
I'll keep my clothing on.

210
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:41,400
You can head back first.

211
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,080
- Go now.
- Yes, Young Lady.

212
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:58,590
What kind of life
does Shangguan Zhi actually lead?

213
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,280
If I keep up the act,

214
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,440
I think my identity will be revealed
one way or another.

215
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,230
By then, I'll end up like her.

216
00:17:05,830 --> 00:17:06,950
There's Master too.

217
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,470
I'm sure he suffered a huge blow

218
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,560
after hearing about my death.

219
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,190
I have to find him.

220
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,190
I need to leave this place by tomorrow

221
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:15,830
no matter what.

222
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:25,470
Zhi?

223
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,070
Zhi,

224
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:37,070
you look much better now.

225
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:39,470
Do you still feel uncomfortable
anywhere in particular?

226
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,070
I've fully recovered.

227
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:42,830
Please...

228
00:17:43,190 --> 00:17:44,680
Lan, please don't worry about me.

229
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,680
I'm glad to hear that.

230
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:47,830
Zhi,

231
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,880
you were in a sorry state

232
00:17:50,190 --> 00:17:51,710
when I saved you.

233
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,350
Who landed you in that plight?

234
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,470
I can't remember.

235
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,590
Anyway, my head hurts

236
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:01,160
when I try to recall the incident.

237
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:01,800
All right, then.

238
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,070
You don't need to recall it.

239
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,190
I shouldn't have asked you about it.

240
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,160
I was just concerned about you.

241
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:13,310
What are they doing?

242
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:14,760
Lan, are you leaving?

243
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,950
Of course we're leaving together.

244
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:18,190
Me too?

245
00:18:18,190 --> 00:18:20,230
Zhi, after I gave it some thought,

246
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:21,830
I think I should bring you
back to the capital with me.

247
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:25,160
I'll hire a famous physician
to help regulate your health.

248
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:26,920
I've packed most of our belongings.

249
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:28,560
We'll depart today.

250
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,280
I cannot leave.

251
00:18:34,110 --> 00:18:34,920
Zhi,

252
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:37,470
Heyang reminds you
of the tragedy you experienced.

253
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:39,190
I always listened to you in the past.

254
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:40,000
Can you listen to me

255
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,280
this time?

256
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,350
Don't worry.

257
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,110
The journey will be slow.

258
00:18:44,280 --> 00:18:45,590
It won't tire you out.

259
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,710
Zhi,

260
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,920
be a good girl.

261
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:15,230
Lan, you kept me company
in Heyang for one month.

262
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:16,710
I'm sure many things were delayed.

263
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:18,470
It must've been tough.

264
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,110
I can make money anytime.

265
00:19:21,430 --> 00:19:22,920
However, I only have one sister.

266
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:39,710
Stop the carriage.

267
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,560
Why are you stopping the carriage?

268
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:45,950
I have an emergency to attend to.

269
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:47,190
All right. I'll join you.

270
00:19:49,470 --> 00:19:51,920
I have a stomach ache.

271
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:53,430
Lan, are you sure you want to join me?

272
00:19:55,190 --> 00:19:56,000
Ling,

273
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:57,280
take good care of the Young Lady.

274
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,040
Yes, Mr. Shangguan.

275
00:19:58,040 --> 00:20:02,100
[Tower of Joy]

276
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:08,830
Try it.

277
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:09,640
It's pretty good.

278
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:12,760
Where are my earrings?

279
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:14,680
It was here just now.
Help me look for it.

280
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:15,590
Yes, Young Lady.

281
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:16,760
Hurry and look for it.

282
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:19,220
How was it? Did you find any clues?

283
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,200
Yeah.

284
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,200
Great.

285
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,250
You should've told me earlier.

286
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:27,470
Young Lady.

287
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:29,760
Young Lady?

288
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:46,260
[Coffin Home]

289
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:00,950
Master.

290
00:21:02,470 --> 00:21:03,280
Master!

291
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,470
Master!

292
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:10,350
Master!

293
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:12,160
Master!

294
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,760
There's blood on the ground.

295
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:29,800
Don't tell me Master was harmed too?

296
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:33,160
I think this looks nice.

297
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:34,350
It looks better than the other one.

298
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:35,640
- This does look exquisite.
- Yeah, right?

299
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:36,830
Have you heard?

300
00:21:36,950 --> 00:21:38,590
The new magistrate
will assume his position today.

301
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,190
The entire Heyang knows about it.

302
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:42,800
I even heard

303
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:45,280
that the new magistrate
is the future prince consort.

304
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,310
How did you find out?

305
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:47,760
The entire Heyang is talking about it.

306
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:48,880
How could you not know?

307
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,310
What are they looking at?

308
00:21:53,470 --> 00:21:54,040
Who is that?

309
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,000
Is that Mr. Pan?

310
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:56,470
Mr. Pan?

311
00:21:57,560 --> 00:22:00,000
That's Mr. Pan!

312
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:05,190
Mr. Pan is actually in Heyang.

313
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:16,830
Mr. Pan actually dyed his hair white.

314
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:24,070
He's the new magistrate?

315
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:26,400
Wasn't Mr. Pan impeached
for forcibly taking a woman

316
00:22:26,590 --> 00:22:28,760
and causing his new wife
to take her own life?

317
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:29,800
How did he become

318
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:31,470
the magistrate of Heyang?

319
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,430
You have no idea.

320
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,350
I just came back from the capital.

321
00:22:35,470 --> 00:22:37,310
I heard that he made acquaintances
with the princess long ago.

322
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:39,830
However, he couldn't marry her
as he had a marriage granted

323
00:22:39,830 --> 00:22:40,830
by the late emperor.

324
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:42,680
Now, they're engaged.

325
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,590
The princess told several
important subjects to recommend him

326
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:47,190
to be a magistrate in Heyang
as a figurehead

327
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:48,310
in the name of mourning his late wife.

328
00:22:48,520 --> 00:22:49,710
When he returns to the imperial court,

329
00:22:49,710 --> 00:22:51,520
we cannot address him as Mr. Pan.

330
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:52,880
You're right.

331
00:22:53,950 --> 00:22:55,520
We have to address him
as prince consort by then.

332
00:22:55,950 --> 00:22:57,160
No wonder.

333
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:59,110
He's just waiting for
his rise to prominence.

334
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,920
He'll be a prince consort
when he goes back.

335
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:04,680
So, he married me and killed me

336
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:07,710
to end the marriage granted
by the late emperor.

337
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,280
Now, he's all set to rise to the top.

338
00:23:10,340 --> 00:23:14,220
♪Liberation or cowardice to let go♪

339
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:18,820
♪Perhaps it's a misstep into your heart,
it's a hasty feeling♪

340
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:22,260
♪It's an unwillingness to be
just a passer-by with you♪

341
00:23:22,380 --> 00:23:26,460
♪Even if I were to die
after a few intense struggles♪

342
00:23:26,580 --> 00:23:29,460
♪I would have lived a life worth living♪

343
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:34,020
♪If grasses and trees are sharp blades,
if mountains and waters are temples♪

344
00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:37,190
I didn't just look for you

345
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:39,430
because I wanted to fulfill
the marriage promise.

346
00:23:39,710 --> 00:23:41,400
I did so because I wanted to find you,

347
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,310
take care of you, and protect you.

348
00:23:44,470 --> 00:23:45,710
No matter if it was ten years ago

349
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,160
or ten years in the future,

350
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,040
you're the only person

351
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:52,110
I want to marry.

352
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:54,560
When he returns to the imperial court,

353
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:56,110
we cannot address him as Mr. Pan.

354
00:23:56,230 --> 00:23:57,920
We have to address him
as Consort Pan by then.

355
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,430
Young Lady!

356
00:24:11,950 --> 00:24:12,470
Zhi.

357
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:13,560
Young Lady!

358
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:14,310
Zhi!

359
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:35,760
Zhi.

360
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,070
What's wrong?

361
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,520
I got lost.

362
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,400
Tell me.

363
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:55,070
Why are you upset?

364
00:24:57,800 --> 00:25:00,110
You were in a hurry
to bring me back to the capital

365
00:25:01,190 --> 00:25:03,110
because you knew Yue was going
to be the new magistrate.

366
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,590
I knew that you just recovered
not long ago.

367
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:20,830
I was worried that you might
be triggered when you see him.

368
00:25:22,110 --> 00:25:22,920
Zhi,

369
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,190
follow me back to the capital.

370
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:27,920
I won't go anywhere.

371
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,880
I only want to stay here.

372
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:33,950
Zhi,

373
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:36,830
I know you have deep feelings
for Pan Yue.

374
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,400
However, some relationships
can't be forced.

375
00:25:39,470 --> 00:25:41,470
There's no need to repeat your mistake.

376
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:45,590
But he has already ruined my life.

377
00:25:51,950 --> 00:25:53,000
I'm sorry,

378
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:56,160
but I have to stay.

379
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:04,560
All right.

380
00:26:05,590 --> 00:26:06,760
I promise you.

381
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:09,520
From now on,

382
00:26:10,230 --> 00:26:11,950
you can stay here for
as long as you want.

383
00:26:13,560 --> 00:26:15,070
You can do whatever you want.

384
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:16,800
I'll follow your will.

385
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:17,830
Really?

386
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,520
But no matter what,

387
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:25,710
you must promise me

388
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:28,430
that you won't run away from home

389
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:31,070
or attempt anything silly,

390
00:26:31,950 --> 00:26:32,760
understood?

391
00:26:45,380 --> 00:26:48,340
[Sunrise Garden]

392
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:52,000
Shangguan Zhi,

393
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:54,830
I cannot forgive you

394
00:26:55,070 --> 00:26:56,470
for what you've done.

395
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:59,310
However, it wasn't my wish
for you to perish

396
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:01,000
because of that.

397
00:27:02,710 --> 00:27:04,520
Now, I'm using your identity.

398
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,760
I know

399
00:27:06,470 --> 00:27:08,680
this is unfair to your elder brother,

400
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,470
but I have no choice.

401
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:16,760
I can only approach Pan Yue
and expose his true colors

402
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,190
by using your identity.

403
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,430
I'm sure you're unhappy

404
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:23,830
with your wrongful death
if you're in the afterlife now.

405
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:26,640
I promise you.

406
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:29,560
I will bring the culprit to justice

407
00:27:30,470 --> 00:27:31,830
so that you can rest in peace.

408
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,950
She likes fresh flowers.

409
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:08,350
She loves to doll herself up,
and she's an attention-seeker, huh?

410
00:28:14,820 --> 00:28:16,460
[Lucky]

411
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:20,230
She's pretty superstitious
for a young girl.

412
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:28,860
[Facial features of a beauty]

413
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:33,470
We do have some similarities.

414
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:40,400
Lifting one's lips,
biting the bottom lip with the upper lip.

415
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:41,710
Make sure none
but eight teeth are visible.

416
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:44,830
By practicing such moves,
you'll win a man's heart with your smile.

417
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:48,800
Yue,

418
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:51,880
how have you been?

419
00:28:56,230 --> 00:28:56,920
Madam,

420
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,160
take a look at these jade bangles.

421
00:28:58,560 --> 00:29:00,110
These are made
with top-quality Nephrite jade.

422
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,920
Look at its glow and design.

423
00:29:01,950 --> 00:29:04,070
There's an elegant air surrounding it.

424
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,880
If a person
of your fair complexion puts it on,

425
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:09,160
people will mistake it
as a part of your fair body.

426
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,350
All right. I'll take this.

427
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:14,800
I wish you health and prosperity!

428
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:15,830
Please come again!

429
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:17,680
Free profit.

430
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:18,350
Miss.

431
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,760
Our Young Lady wishes
to check out your collection.

432
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:22,590
Come with me.

433
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,350
Okay.

434
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:26,950
Sister, keep an eye on my stool for me.

435
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:27,640
Don't let anyone steal it.

436
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:28,470
All right.

437
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,430
Young Lady,

438
00:29:34,190 --> 00:29:35,000
she's here.

439
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,880
Ling, buy some food for me.

440
00:29:49,950 --> 00:29:50,800
Yes, Young Lady.

441
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:01,000
Miss, do you wish
to buy some accessories?

442
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,470
Miss, you have excellent taste.

443
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:15,070
These are made
with top-quality Nephrite jade.

444
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:16,880
Look at its glow and design.

445
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:21,310
What are you doing?

446
00:30:23,430 --> 00:30:26,000
These are made with low-quality minerals
that have been dyed.

447
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:29,430
You mined the minerals
at the bottom of the Southern Mountain.

448
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,000
You bought the dye
from the Ghost Market.

449
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:32,880
It may not be obvious usually,

450
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:35,070
but the color will surely fade
when it's heated.

451
00:30:36,350 --> 00:30:36,800
You...

452
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:38,310
You...

453
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:40,350
Who are you?

454
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:42,470
I'm Yang Caiwei.

455
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:46,760
You're Yang?

456
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:51,760
It's me.

457
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:56,160
How did you become like this?

458
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,400
As I don't have much time,

459
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,110
I'll explain the situation to you
next time.

460
00:31:00,230 --> 00:31:01,520
Sheng, the coffin home was raided.

461
00:31:01,520 --> 00:31:02,680
And, Master is missing.

462
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:03,760
I think you're a resourceful girl.

463
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:05,040
Can you do some inquiries for me?

464
00:31:07,280 --> 00:31:08,070
It's me.

465
00:31:09,190 --> 00:31:10,280
Are you truly Yang?

466
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,950
I'm glad that you're okay.

467
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,110
I thought something happened to you.

468
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:18,640
I was so upset, you know?

469
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:19,640
It's fine.

470
00:31:19,800 --> 00:31:20,640
Everything's fine.

471
00:31:20,710 --> 00:31:21,520
It's me.

472
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:23,680
Young Lady.

473
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,950
Regarding the things I told you,
you must keep it a secret.

474
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:30,800
Young Lady,

475
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:32,280
I'm done.

476
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:37,160
Heyang is a desolate place indeed.

477
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,590
I shouldn't have wasted my time
viewing such subpar accessories.

478
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:43,800
So what if you're rich?

479
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:44,950
Does that mean you can bully us?

480
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,350
It's fine if you don't want
to buy my wares.

481
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:48,070
But why did you have to smash them?

482
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,470
Ling,

483
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,830
pay her ten times the money.

484
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,350
Yes, Young Lady.

485
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:15,400
Yang is rich now.

486
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:17,760
This is great.

487
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,110
After one month of separation,

488
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,880
I didn't expect you to return.

489
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:26,800
Regarding the incident with Miss Yang,

490
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,110
you don't need to pay heed
to the rumors out there.

491
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,070
After all, they don't know you well.

492
00:32:35,590 --> 00:32:37,880
She's already gone. There's no need
to mention her name again.

493
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:42,230
Heyang is notorious for its hostility.

494
00:32:42,230 --> 00:32:44,430
I heard that the previous magistrates

495
00:32:44,430 --> 00:32:45,560
who wanted to achieve something here

496
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,000
all left

497
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,070
within six months.

498
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:50,280
But you came here of your own accord.

499
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:52,800
Do you have other plans in mind?

500
00:32:54,950 --> 00:32:56,880
Indeed. There's something
I must do here.

501
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:59,710
However, it's a long story.

502
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:01,350
You can return to the capital

503
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,710
and manage your business first.

504
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,950
I'll tell you the details
when I have the chance.

505
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:06,070
Okay.

506
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:07,830
Just tell me

507
00:33:08,070 --> 00:33:09,160
if there's anything you need me to do.

508
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:11,470
I need you to do one thing now.

509
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:12,800
Tell me, then.

510
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,680
Didn't you say you wanted
to offer me a toast?

511
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:17,040
I've been waiting for it
for a long time.

512
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:19,430
All right.

513
00:33:20,430 --> 00:33:21,110
Come.

514
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:34,400
Zhi,

515
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:36,400
do you feel better?

516
00:33:36,710 --> 00:33:37,800
What are you doing here?

517
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,680
We have to return to the capital
tomorrow morning.

518
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:41,400
You should rest well now.

519
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:42,470
Lan, don't worry.

520
00:33:43,470 --> 00:33:44,470
I wish to speak with Yue

521
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:46,830
before we leave.

522
00:33:48,230 --> 00:33:48,800
Okay.

523
00:33:49,310 --> 00:33:50,430
Go ahead, then.

524
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:03,800
I've managed to escape from death
and reflect upon my actions.

525
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,470
I've figured most of the things out.

526
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:10,430
Some relationships cannot be forced.

527
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:14,040
I feel ashamed
for all the ridiculous things

528
00:34:14,390 --> 00:34:15,520
that I've done.

529
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,600
I shouldn't have been obsessed with love

530
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:18,280
and been willful

531
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:19,520
without considering
other people's feelings.

532
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:20,230
Therefore,

533
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,840
I hereby apologize to you.

534
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,600
I accept your apology.

535
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:26,950
Please go back.

536
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:27,950
No.

537
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,520
I don't think an apology is enough.

538
00:34:40,900 --> 00:34:42,600
[Lusted for men, I was willful]

539
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,400
[I had no virtues,
and my life was empty]

540
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:46,020
[Now, I've been reborn]

541
00:34:46,020 --> 00:34:48,020
[I shall punish the evil
and praise the good]

542
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,600
In the past, I was
too stubborn to change.

543
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,150
You won't believe me
no matter what I tell you.

544
00:34:54,950 --> 00:34:56,000
Therefore, this time,

545
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:58,870
I've written them down
with my blood to prove my sincerity.

546
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:01,120
Each of your words was filled
with your blood and tears, huh?

547
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,600
You did put a lot of effort into them.

548
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:04,630
You rested for one month,

549
00:35:04,950 --> 00:35:06,520
yet it seemed like
you could write well now.

550
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:09,600
It's just

551
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,470
that the phrase "punish the evil
and praise the good" is...

552
00:35:13,390 --> 00:35:15,800
This time, I almost died.

553
00:35:16,390 --> 00:35:17,520
We should treat other people
as we would ourselves.

554
00:35:17,910 --> 00:35:19,760
Plenty of disasters have occurred here,

555
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,560
and there are plenty
of dead bodies uncared for.

556
00:35:22,470 --> 00:35:23,280
Yue,

557
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:25,120
I know you came here

558
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:26,320
to rectify Heyang.

559
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:27,000
Therefore,

560
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:29,000
I wish to join the county office
and help you out.

561
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:31,150
I wish to contribute to your cause.

562
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:33,950
If crooks can be brought to justice

563
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:36,080
and the people can live in peace,

564
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:38,280
my revival will be worth it.

565
00:35:41,950 --> 00:35:42,910
Yue,

566
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,430
Mr. Pan,

567
00:35:44,950 --> 00:35:46,560
please give me a chance.

568
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:50,600
I don't care even if I have
to become an errand girl.

569
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:51,950
I'll surely put down the past

570
00:35:51,950 --> 00:35:53,040
and not cause trouble for you two again.

571
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,870
I'm touched

572
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,840
by Zhi's resolve.

573
00:36:03,230 --> 00:36:04,080
Initially, I wanted to bring

574
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,470
her back to the capital with me
tomorrow morning.

575
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,230
But Zhi is truly sincere about this.

576
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:10,840
Even the heavens

577
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,760
can bear witness to her sincerity.

578
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,470
No matter how heartless you are,

579
00:36:15,950 --> 00:36:17,320
you should be shaken by that.

580
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,080
You're right.

581
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,120
She's sincere indeed.

582
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,190
No matter how heartless I am,

583
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:28,430
I have to be shaken by her speech.

584
00:36:32,470 --> 00:36:34,360
Every dog has its day indeed.

585
00:36:35,390 --> 00:36:35,950
Come.

586
00:36:38,190 --> 00:36:39,000
Here's a toast to you.

587
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:41,760
It's my token of sincerity.

588
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:47,560
No need for that.

589
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:48,600
This is necessary.

590
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,080
No need...

591
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:03,150
You should go back
and improve your blood letter.

592
00:37:03,950 --> 00:37:05,230
At least the first four sentences

593
00:37:05,950 --> 00:37:08,390
were concise and impactful.

594
00:37:09,870 --> 00:37:11,080
Thank you for the hospitality.

595
00:37:11,430 --> 00:37:12,520
I shall take my leave now.

596
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:13,760
May you have a smooth trip tomorrow.

597
00:37:21,470 --> 00:37:22,280
Ling.

598
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,600
Let them finish their conversation.

599
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,520
Pan Yue.

600
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:28,670
Pan Yue, you mustn't leave.

601
00:37:29,710 --> 00:37:30,840
I have a question for you.

602
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:34,910
You're avoiding me

603
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,150
all because you want
to marry the princess, right?

604
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:40,520
What did you say?

605
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:42,630
Am I wrong?

606
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:45,000
You're showing me the cold shoulder

607
00:37:45,390 --> 00:37:47,080
while you bow to the princess

608
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,150
and please her in any way you can.

609
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,800
You said

610
00:37:49,910 --> 00:37:51,870
you didn't care
about beauty or wealth, huh?

611
00:37:52,470 --> 00:37:54,430
I didn't expect you to desire something
that was even more vulgar.

612
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,520
It's a shame that I wasn't born
into the imperial family.

613
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,320
I couldn't help you to ascend the ranks.

614
00:38:00,630 --> 00:38:02,760
It's a shame that Yang Caiwei
has to become your stepping stone,

615
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,150
even though she died not long ago.

616
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,630
You're just better-looking than average.

617
00:38:07,950 --> 00:38:09,080
What gives you the right
to bully people?

618
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:11,190
You trampled upon my feelings for you

619
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:14,910
and acted nonchalantly about it.

620
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:17,000
You may look like a glorious person,

621
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,670
but you're a rotten egg inside!

622
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:20,630
Pan Yue, what did I do

623
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:21,760
for you to treat me like this?

624
00:38:21,870 --> 00:38:23,150
I was leading a great life before this.

625
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:25,150
Why did you have to appear
in front of me?

626
00:38:25,190 --> 00:38:26,430
Why must you treat me like this?

627
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:27,950
Why?

628
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:32,910
Shangguan Zhi,

629
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,760
I didn't know

630
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:38,630
that you had such a sharp tongue.

631
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:42,230
Diplomacy before violence, huh?

632
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,150
What did you expect to get from me

633
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:47,800
with this devious plot of yours?

634
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:53,040
I just want to help you out
in the county office.

635
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:55,710
Can you even believe your own words?

636
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:57,630
Listen.

637
00:38:58,360 --> 00:39:00,760
You better return
to the capital immediately.

638
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:03,320
Do not mention her name again.

639
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,670
Don't try to challenge my patience.

640
00:39:07,230 --> 00:39:08,040
If not,

641
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:11,360
even I don't know what I'll do to you.

642
00:39:16,870 --> 00:39:17,430
Zhi.

643
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,950
- Young Lady!
- Are you okay?

644
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:20,000
- Young Lady!
- Zhi!

645
00:39:20,910 --> 00:39:21,710
Are you okay?

646
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,520
Pan Yue,

647
00:39:26,710 --> 00:39:27,710
you crossed the line.

648
00:39:33,470 --> 00:39:35,230
I deserved it.

649
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,470
It's not his fault.

650
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:38,430
Although Zhi has a hasty temper,

651
00:39:38,630 --> 00:39:40,390
