652
00:39:40,390 --> 00:39:42,190
It's not like she's a villain.

653
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:43,670
Why are you treating her like this?

654
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,040
Pan Yue,

655
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:52,520
you know this too.

656
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,360
She's my only sister.

657
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:57,320
I gave her everything she wanted
since young.

658
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:58,800
You know fully well

659
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:00,390
how I treated her with care.

660
00:40:01,430 --> 00:40:03,280
She was indeed insensible
when she was young.

661
00:40:03,470 --> 00:40:04,870
But now, she's all grown up.

662
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:06,950
She's willing to turn over a new leaf.

663
00:40:06,950 --> 00:40:08,470
Can't you just give her a chance?

664
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,560
And

665
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,040
she just recovered not long ago.

666
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:12,320
How could you make her

667
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,560
this agitated?

668
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,360
Will you be able to sleep in peace

669
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,710
if something happens to her?

670
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,600
Fine.

671
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:27,390
Since you already said that,

672
00:40:28,870 --> 00:40:30,190
I'll give her one last chance.

673
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:34,840
Ling,

674
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:38,040
